<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SolarSight AI — 太陽光発電 AI管理システム</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@300;400;500;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --green: #1D9E75;
  --green-light: #E1F5EE;
  --green-dark: #0F6E56;
  --amber: #EF9F27;
  --red: #E24B4A;
  --gray-50: #F8F8F6;
  --gray-100: #F1EFE8;
  --gray-200: #D3D1C7;
  --gray-400: #888780;
  --gray-700: #444441;
  --gray-900: #1A1A18;
  --white: #ffffff;
}

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
  background: var(--gray-900);
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1.7;
}

a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

.hero {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.hero::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(29,158,117,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.grid-bg {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  pointer-events: none;
}

.badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  background: rgba(29,158,117,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(29,158,117,0.3);
  color: #5DCAA5;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 6px 16px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.badge-dot {
  width: 6px;
  height: 6px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: #5DCAA5;
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50% { opacity: 0.3; }
}

.hero h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.hero h1 span {
  color: var(--green);
}

.hero p {
  font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
  color: var(--gray-400);
  max-width: 600px;
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.btn-group {
  display: flex;
  gap: 16px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
}

.btn-primary {
  background: var(--green);
  color: white;
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  font-family: inherit;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.2s;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
}
.btn-primary:hover { background: var(--green-dark); }

.btn-outline {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--gray-200);
  padding: 14px 32px;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 400;
  font-family: inherit;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: border-color 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
}
.btn-outline:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); color: white; }

.scroll-hint {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 2rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-size: 12px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 8px;
  animation: bounce 2s infinite;
}
@keyframes bounce { 0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(6px)} }

.section {
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.section-label {
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  color: var(--green);
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

.section-title {
  font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 3rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.section-sub {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  max-width: 560px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.divider {
  border: none;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}

.stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: 4rem 2rem;
}

.stat {
  background: var(--gray-900);
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.stat .num {
  font-size: 3rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--green);
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}

.stat .lbl {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-weight: 300;
}

.flow {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: 0;
  position: relative;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.flow-step {
  padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
  position: relative;
  text-align: center;
}

.flow-step::after {
  content: '→';
  position: absolute;
  right: -12px;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-size: 20px;
  z-index: 1;
}

.flow-step:last-child::after { display: none; }

.step-num {
  width: 40px;
  height: 40px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(29,158,117,0.15);
  border: 1px solid rgba(29,158,117,0.3);
  color: var(--green);
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin: 0 auto 1rem;
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
}

.step-title {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 6px;
}

.step-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-weight: 300;
}

.features {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  border-radius: 16px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.feature {
  background: var(--gray-900);
  padding: 2rem;
  transition: background 0.2s;
}

.feature:hover { background: rgba(29,158,117,0.05); }

.feature-icon {
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  background: rgba(29,158,117,0.12);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  font-size: 20px;
}

.feature h3 {
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.feature p {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-weight: 300;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.panel-demo {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.panel-demo-title {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
}

.panel-grid-demo {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(16, 1fr);
  gap: 3px;
}

.pc {
  aspect-ratio: 1;
  border-radius: 2px;
}

.pc.ok { background: var(--green); opacity: 0.8; }
.pc.warn { background: var(--amber); }
.pc.err { background: var(--red); }
.pc.off { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }

.legend-demo {
  display: flex;
  gap: 20px;
  margin-top: 1rem;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
}

.legend-demo span {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
}

.legend-demo i {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 2px;
  display: inline-block;
}

.tech-stack {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr));
  gap: 12px;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.tech-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 1.2rem;
  text-align: center;
}

.tech-card .tech-name {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 500;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--green);
}

.tech-card .tech-role {
  font-size: 11px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
}

.pricing {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 3rem;
}

.price-card {
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 2rem;
  position: relative;
}

.price-card.featured {
  border-color: rgba(29,158,117,0.4);
  background: rgba(29,158,117,0.05);
}

.price-badge {
  position: absolute;
  top: -12px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  background: var(--green);
  color: white;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 500;
  padding: 4px 16px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  white-space: nowrap;
}

.price-plan {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.price-amount {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  color: var(--white);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: 4px;
}

.price-amount span {
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 400;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
}

.price-desc {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}

.price-features {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 10px;
}

.price-features li {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: var(--gray-200);
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  gap: 8px;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.price-features li::before {
  content: '✓';
  color: var(--green);
  font-weight: 500;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: 1px;
}

.cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 6rem 2rem;
  position: relative;
}

.cta::before {
  content: '';
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 50% 50%, rgba(29,158,117,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.cta h2 {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -0.02em;
}

.cta p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: var(--gray-400);
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 300;
}

footer {
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  padding: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
  font-size: 12px;
  color: var(--gray-400);
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="badge"><span class="badge-dot"></span> AI ドローン点検システム</div>
  <h1>太陽光発電を<br><span>AIでまるごと管理。</span></h1>
  <p>ドローン撮影画像をアップロードするだけで、AIがパネルの異常を自動検知。発電量・売電収益・点検レポートをひとつの画面で完結します。</p>
  <div class="btn-group">
    <%= link_to "ダッシュボードへ", dashboard_path, class: "btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to "点検を始める", new_inspection_path, class: "btn-outline" %>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <span>スクロール</span>
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/></svg>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<div class="stats">
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="num">94<span style="font-size:1.5rem">%</span></div>
    <div class="lbl">AI異常検知精度</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="num">0.1<span style="font-size:1.5rem">秒</span></div>
    <div class="lbl">画像1枚あたりの解析時間</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="num">70<span style="font-size:1.5rem">%</span></div>
    <div class="lbl">点検コスト削減効果</div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <div class="num">24<span style="font-size:1rem">時間</span></div>
    <div class="lbl">365日リアルタイム監視</div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="divider">

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">使い方はシンプル。<br>たった4ステップ。</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">専門知識は不要。ドローンで撮影して画像をアップロードするだけで、あとはAIが全部やります。</p>

  <div class="flow">
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <div class="step-title">ドローンで撮影</div>
      <div class="step-desc">発電施設の上空をドローンで飛行し、パネルを撮影します</div>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <div class="step-title">画像をアップロード</div>
      <div class="step-desc">管理画面にドラッグ＆ドロップするだけでOK</div>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <div class="step-title">AIが自動解析</div>
      <div class="step-desc">異常・汚れ・傷を数秒で検出してレポート生成</div>
    </div>
    <div class="flow-step">
      <div class="step-num">04</div>
      <div class="step-title">ダッシュボードに反映</div>
      <div class="step-desc">全パネルの状態・収益・履歴を一元管理</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="panel-demo">
    <div class="panel-demo-title">// リアルタイム パネル状態マップ</div>
    <div class="panel-grid-demo" id="panelDemoGrid"></div>
    <div class="legend-demo">
      <span><i style="background:var(--green);opacity:0.8"></i>正常</span>
      <span><i style="background:var(--amber)"></i>要注意</span>
      <span><i style="background:var(--red)"></i>異常検知</span>
      <span><i style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08)"></i>停止中</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">Features</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">管理に必要な機能を<br>すべて搭載。</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">発電量のモニタリングから売電収益の管理、AIによる異常検知まで、ひとつのシステムで完結します。</p>

  <div class="features">
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">📸</div>
      <h3>ドローン画像AI解析</h3>
      <p>撮影画像をアップロードするだけで、AIがホットスポット・汚れ・クラック・変色を自動検知し、対処法レポートを自動生成します。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">📈</div>
      <h3>発電量リアルタイム監視</h3>
      <p>日・月・年単位の発電量推移をグラフで可視化。目標値との比較や異常な発電低下を即座に検出します。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">💴</div>
      <h3>売電収益管理</h3>
      <p>月次の売電量・収益を自動集計。前月比・年間推移をひと目で把握でき、経営判断に必要な数字をすぐに確認できます。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🗺️</div>
      <h3>パネル状態マップ</h3>
      <p>全パネルの状態を色分けしたマップ表示。異常パネルの場所を直感的に把握でき、クリックで詳細と対処法を確認できます。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔔</div>
      <h3>異常アラート通知</h3>
      <p>異常検知時にメール・LINE通知を即座に送信。現地確認が必要な場合は優先度付きで担当者に自動通知します。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">📄</div>
      <h3>点検レポート自動生成</h3>
      <p>点検履歴・異常内容・対処状況を自動でレポート化。PDF出力に対応し、社内共有や記録保管に活用できます。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">Technology</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">最新AIを活用した<br>信頼性の高い技術基盤。</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">業界標準の技術スタックで構築し、スケーラブルで安定した運用が可能です。</p>

  <div class="tech-stack">
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">Claude AI</div>
      <div class="tech-role">画像解析・レポート生成</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">Ruby on Rails</div>
      <div class="tech-role">バックエンド・API</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">PostgreSQL</div>
      <div class="tech-role">データベース</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">Hotwire</div>
      <div class="tech-role">リアルタイムUI</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">AWS S3</div>
      <div class="tech-role">画像ストレージ</div>
    </div>
    <div class="tech-card">
      <div class="tech-name">Render</div>
      <div class="tech-role">クラウドホスティング</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<hr class="divider">

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">Pricing</div>
  <h2 class="section-title">シンプルな料金体系。</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">初期導入から本番運用まで、規模に合わせたプランをご用意しています。</p>

  <div class="pricing">
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-plan">スターター プラン</div>
      <div class="price-amount">¥30<span>万円〜</span></div>
      <div class="price-desc">プロトタイプ・デモ納品</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li>ダッシュボードUI</li>
        <li>AI画像解析機能</li>
        <li>パネル状態マップ</li>
        <li>点検レポート生成</li>
        <li>発電量グラフ</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="price-card featured">
      <div class="price-badge">おすすめ</div>
      <div class="price-plan">スタンダード プラン</div>
      <div class="price-amount">¥100<span>万円〜</span></div>
      <div class="price-desc">本番システム導入</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li>スタータープランの全機能</li>
        <li>売電収益管理</li>
        <li>アラート・通知機能</li>
        <li>複数発電所対応</li>
        <li>PDF出力・レポート管理</li>
        <li>Renderへのデプロイ込み</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-plan">保守・運用プラン</div>
      <div class="price-amount">¥5<span>万円/月〜</span></div>
      <div class="price-desc">納品後の継続サポート</div>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li>不具合対応・修正</li>
        <li>機能追加・改善</li>
        <li>AIモデルの精度改善</li>
        <li>月次レポート提供</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <h2>まずはデモを<br>ご覧ください。</h2>
  <p>実際に動くプロトタイプをご用意しています。<br>お気軽にお問い合わせください。</p>
